item.title: Mon, 9 Dec 2024 12:29:34 UTC
item.description:
Hi Folks,
I am slowly regaining the ability to work on the repository.
It's going to take me a while to upgrade slackware,
fix everything and then compile pretty much the whole repository.
But something is moving.
Let me know if you know of any problems with new updates, patches, etc.
Thank you all, and please forgive the long absence. Happy Slack!
